'''Grace''' is the neighbor of [[Annie Banks]].

==History==
After not seeing her neighbor, Annie, get her newspaper in the morning as she did like clockwork, Grace suspected something had happened. She peeked over the wall separating their houses and saw Annie tangled in razor wire in her yard. So she called 911 and the first responders broke down the gate and took Annie to the hospital.
